room_title: Escape room "Asylum Escape" by Castle of Chaos in Salt Lake City
room_description:
You have been taken captive inside a mad doctor’s asylum. You and up to 8 total guests must first escape your cells, the hall and then the mad doctor’s exam room.
One lucky guest will be asked to wear a straight jacket and start the room in an isolated cell. (no one has to wear it, but it makes it more fun!)
